sequenceDiagram
  participant User
  participant Gateway
  participant Auth
  participant API
  participant DB
  User->>Gateway: POST /login
  Gateway->>Auth: validateCredentials()
  alt valid credentials
    Auth-->>Gateway: JWT token
    Gateway-->>User: 200 OK + token
    User->>Gateway: GET /orders
    Gateway->>Auth: verifyToken()
    Auth-->>Gateway: valid
    Gateway->>API: fetchOrders()
    API->>DB: SELECT * FROM orders
    DB-->>API: rows
    API-->>Gateway: JSON array
    Gateway-->>User: 200 OK
  else invalid credentials
    Auth-->>Gateway: 401
    Gateway-->>User: 401 Unauthorized
  end
  Note over User,Gateway: Session established
  par Background Tasks
    API->>DB: UPDATE metrics
  and Cleanup
    Auth->>Auth: pruneExpiredTokens()
  end
